Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:17.00,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}ささやく祈り
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:20.80,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}ゆがんだ景色を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:24.92,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}君となぞって行く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:29.01,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}「本当」を求め
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:33.14,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}うそでもいいから なんてね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:37.23,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}見透かし合うように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:41.02,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}辿ってゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:45.19,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}Looking for 言葉超えた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:49.20,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}落ちて行く 羽のように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:51.99,ed_jp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}Looking for 見つけて
